               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalota ʿǝṭan “Prayer of Incense” (fols. 5ra-57vb)
 - Prayer of
                     Incense for Sunday (ʿǝlätä ʾǝḥud) (fols. 40va-55vb) 
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
