                           parchment guards.</decoNote>
                        <decoNote xml:id="b5">Blind tooled ornaments on the reddish-brown leather
                           cover (5 tools were used: double line fillet, double circle, cross
                           hatching, triple sine wave, x-form with dot).</decoNote>
                     </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
