               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0049QSM">Qarsabar Mikāʾel / QSM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1937" notAfter="1938">Text I mentions on <locus target="#57v">57v</locus> the names of Archbishop ʾAbrǝham (archbishop of
                        Ethiopia in 1937-38, mentioned also on <locus target="#27rb">27rb</locus>)
                        and Bishop Marqos (officially bishop of Eritrea and Tǝgray in 1937-41, but
                        unofficially until 1951 and his appointment as bishop of Eritrea, mentioned
                        also on <locus target="#33ra">33ra</locus>).</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>According to Additio 2, the Ms. was donated
                     by rās Gabra Mädhǝn.
 On 57vb, the name of the original donor has been
                     erased.</provenance></history>
